{"tid":739980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人細個嘅時候超驚「大頭佛」？","createTime":"2018-07-12T13:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T18:39:07.000Z","uid":90457,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f4300c811b519f9bf6e678b0bd3da10ff399b43e","tid":739980,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"唔放圖喇，就算大個睇見都有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之細個第一次見到覺得好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n15-16年前了，嗰陣係過年前啦，讀幼稚園嘅時候啲老師唔知我驚呢味嘢，喺全部同學面前突然將個頭罩喺背後拎出嚟，仲叫啲同學逐個排隊摸個頭罩，我一路話唔要唔要，連睇都唔咁睇，條隊排到我嗰陣我真係驚到喊<br />\n<br />\n「後來就明白」，啲老師知道成件事搞大咗就叫我呀媽嚟安撫返我情緒，係有講對唔住，不過由呢件事之後直到小四左右，我一直好驚農曆新年，每逢跟父母去親戚屋企拜年一見到有舞獅就即刻拎轉面衝返入去，「爸爸我唔想再見到嗰個人頭啊。。。」，因為我知舞獅一出現，好快見到嗰個頭罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據我呀媽口述同細個嘅記憶，嗰段期間啲幼稚園同學一講「大頭仔」「大頭妹」我就情緒失控"},{"pid":"5baf034e7779dc2a34f4d41f3b34a10c4abc8b03","tid":739980,"uid":51250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"ea007ffafde31c9fec405723f583be99980ed90a","tid":739980,"uid":82749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"打咁大段野<br />\n以為故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed5d1bc8e6d8ad38714ec7100afa0dd45dd4ee2","tid":739980,"uid":126796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"534d864479f3a32f5af0b437edf7a5017c9e2b2f","tid":739980,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"fb9d192627c08a480309136a76be2f9cdf079b0c","tid":739980,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"每次都有衝動走去大頭彿背後踢佢屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81029faa2dd44b351d017447cbee52b881019c79","tid":739980,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"麥當勞叔叔仲得人驚啦"},{"pid":"0b6ee49fd3426bac9246af6b3025495218593ad8","tid":739980,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9d192627c08a480309136a76be2f9cdf079b0c","tid":739980,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"每次都有衝動走去大頭彿背後踢佢屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"細個仲傻到擰轉面大喊、叫個獅首一啖咬走個頭罩佢，唔想再見到個頭罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f962920b35a010b4b37b79f786ee4224d5623ef0","tid":739980,"uid":90457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"81029faa2dd44b351d017447cbee52b881019c79","tid":739980,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"麥當勞叔叔仲得人驚啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"因為麥當勞叔叔係一個人像<br />\n而我第一次見到大頭佛頭罩，係俾人除低咗，<span style=\"color: red;\">得返個頭</span>擺喺地下，嗰個碩大嘅首級同埋冇眼珠嘅空洞眼窩"},{"pid":"3df644d67a38bdc506bfdd5fd5fc363c47dbf717","tid":739980,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"隻獅子頭我都驚"},{"pid":"1af70a5027ec496ac75725932f0b3adb96dc0e5f","tid":739980,"uid":45105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人放圖"},{"pid":"1a6b89931090db0f6045519188b6d386d6161003","tid":739980,"uid":194552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"dafc5c2e8c7afb2581488a81e0d7afc4c00b71ef","tid":739980,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"今晚戴住個大頭佛訓包你克服到呢個恐懼"},{"pid":"2ddb9cd61faf85d5416d1592bc325c6ef5f306ed","tid":739980,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"d7f1c10ffafbf4a539a1d52ad13f510ae1246f84","tid":739980,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"想聽鬼故 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e179631f6da9becb3eeaa9b7173820fe701e58","tid":739980,"uid":9362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"恐怖谷理論"},{"pid":"099ab9fcd6855246dfd82c88775b53dda027654c","tid":739980,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df5580899a18a00f347a405db2a1f5a95eef5e1","tid":739980,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:33:07.000Z","msg":"要更正<br />\n個頭罩俾人戴緊其實唔恐怖，甚至可以話幾得意，扭嚟扭去<br />\n<br />\n恐怖在佢靜態嘅本身，雖然佢郁都唔郁，但係形住形住喺冇人嘅時候，佢會偷望自己，而當我走埋去佢面前，明明一直存在嘅笑容、一下子變得生動起嚟，明明對耳係聽唔到有聲<br />\n<br />\n「但係個腦喺唔受自己控制下，話俾我知嗰隻嘢係笑緊，但我依然聽唔到有笑聲」<br />\n<br />\n呢個係細個嘅經驗，應該只係疑心生暗鬼啦"},{"pid":"6b550099e6e73020454c94d8ffdb36e87cc64574","tid":739980,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df644d67a38bdc506bfdd5fd5fc363c47dbf717","tid":739980,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"隻獅子頭我都驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"個獅子頭我又唔驚，個樣幾好笑幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8db50c9d08d61ae4e094a9a8818b1c0ed3cd771","tid":739980,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:37:18.000Z","msg":"唔好禁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%B4%E4%BD%9B.jpg/1200px-%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%B4%E4%BD%9B.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe5%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A4%25B4%25E4%25BD%259B.jpg%2F1200px-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A4%25B4%2